OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmurder and cruelty of his partner's
OL,8,Ftoddler who was left in his care.
OL,10,FCharlie Roberts was aged one year and
OL,11,F10 months when he suffered an
OL,12,Funsurvivable head injury, which
OL,13,Fprosecutors claimed during a trial was
OL,14,Fcaused by Christopher Stockton shaking
OL,15,For throwing him.
OL,17,FThe 38-year-old had stayed up late
OL,18,Fplaying video games the night before
OL,19,Ftoddler Charlie was left in his care
OL,20,Fon 12 January while his mother went
OL,21,Fout to an eye appointment.
