OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FStockton, of Neasham Road, denied
OL,7,Fmurder but was convicted at trial by a
OL,8,Fjury at Teesside Crown Court on
OL,9,FTuesday (10 December).
OL,11,FHe was also found guilty of a charge
OL,12,Fof child cruelty, for injuries caused
OL,13,Fto Charlie in the months before his
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FCharlie's mother and Stockton's then
OL,17,Fpartner, Paula Roberts, 41, of Close
OL,18,FStreet, Darlington, previously pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to child neglect after failing
OL,20,Fto act over a number of painful
OL,21,Finjuries suffered by her son.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
