OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FStockton, who had moved in with
OL,7,FRoberts and her little boy just seven
OL,8,Fdays earlier, was in sole charge of
OL,9,FCharlie when he inflicted a severe
OL,10,Fhead injury which caused widespread
OL,11,Fbleeding on the brain.
OL,13,FNicholas Lumley KC, prosecuting, told
OL,14,Fjurors: "The prosecution say that
OL,15,FChristopher Stockton ` and nobody else
OL,16,F` is responsible for Charlie's death;
OL,17,Fthat he shook or threw him with such
OL,18,Fviolence, deliberately and forcefully
OL,19,Fharming little Charlie."
