OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FThe mother had left the home minutes
OL,7,Fbefore to go for an eye test and
OL,8,FStockton, who was off work ill and who
OL,9,Fhad stayed up into the early hours
OL,10,Fplaying Xbox games, must have snapped
OL,11,Fthat January morning at the family
OL,12,Fhome in Darlington.
OL,14,FStockton rang 999 and could be heard
OL,15,Fon a recording repeatedly saying "come
OL,16,Fon mate" and "wakey wakey" to the
OL,17,Flittle boy, who was not breathing.
