OL,6,FThe toddler died in hospital the next
OL,7,Fday.
OL,9,FAn excerpt of Stockton's 999 call,
OL,10,Freleased by the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService (CPS), was played to the jury
OL,13,FRoberts pleaded guilty to neglect
OL,14,Fduring the trial.
OL,16,FShe admitted failing to seek medical
OL,17,Fhelp for her little boy in December
OL,18,F2023 and January this year after he
OL,19,Fsuffered injuries to his private parts
OL,20,Fand to his ear.
