OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FJurors were told that Charlie suffered
OL,7,Fbruising in the months before his
OL,8,Fdeath.
OL,10,FIn August, five months prior to his
OL,11,Fmurder, Roberts expressed concerns to
OL,12,Fher brother about Stockton and said
OL,13,Fshe had installed the spy camera,
OL,14,Fhidden in a pot plant.
OL,16,FCharlie's natural father saw his son
OL,17,Fonce a week and was described by the
OL,18,Fprosecution as "loving and caring".
