OL,6,FSocial services were concerned about
OL,7,Fthe little boy's welfare at home with
OL,8,Fhis mother after he was taken to
OL,9,Fhospital in May 2023 with bruising,
OL,10,Fbut no action was taken at the time.
OL,12,FRoberts tried to explain that bruises
OL,13,Fon Charlie's ear months later were
OL,14,Fcaused by him resting on his toy box
OL,15,Fwhile he was sleep-walking or from
OL,16,Ffalling out of bed.
OL,18,FThe CPS has released this footage from
OL,19,FChristopher Stockton's police
OL,20,Finterview, which has been shown to the
OL,21,Fjury
