OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FDr Deborah Stalker, an expert
OL,7,Fpaediatrician and specialist in child
OL,8,Fprotection, studied photos of Charlie
OL,9,Fwhile was alive, medical experts and
OL,10,Fpost-mortem images.
OL,12,FShe told the jury she did not believe
OL,13,Fthat Charlie suffered a bruised ear
OL,14,Fwhile sleep-walking.
OL,16,FShe said: "In my opinion, this is a
OL,17,Fnon-accidental injury, by that I mean
OL,18,Fit is a purposefully-inflicted injury.
OL,20,F"Accidental injuries to the ear are
OL,21,Fvery rare."
