OL,6,FMr Justice Goss will sentence the pair
OL,7,Fnext month, once reports have been
OL,8,Fprepared on Roberts.
OL,10,FStockton was told that a life sentence
OL,11,Fwas inevitable, with the judge needing
OL,12,Fto set a minimum term.
OL,14,FThe judge thanked the jury for their
OL,15,F"care" in dealing with this "upsetting
OL,16,Fcase".
