OL,6,FOutside court, Charlie's dad Barry
OL,7,FGreenwell said: "Charlie was a much-
OL,8,Floved son and grandson who has been
OL,9,Ftaken away needlessly and has left the
OL,10,Fwhole family with a void that will
OL,11,Fnever be filled.
OL,13,F"As a family we are processing the
OL,14,Frecent events and are trying to come
OL,15,Fto terms with the verdict and
OL,16,Finformation given that has been deeply
OL,17,Fdisturbing to ourselves."
