OL,6,FHe added: "Our thoughts remain with
OL,7,Fthe father of Charlie Roberts, for who
OL,8,Fthis must remain a particularly
OL,9,Fdifficult time. We sincerely hope that
OL,10,Fhe can take some measure of comfort
OL,11,Ffrom today's conviction of Christopher
OL,12,FStockton over the death of his son."
OL,14,FDetective Superintendent Chris Barker,
OL,15,Fwho led the inquiry, said:
OL,16,F"Christopher Stockton was entrusted
OL,17,Fwith caring for Charlie on the morning
OL,18,Fof Friday, 12 January.
