OL,6,F"It was his responsibility to keep
OL,7,FCharlie safe. He didn't do that. He is
OL,8,Fthe only person who knows exactly what
OL,9,Fhappened that morning but what we do
OL,10,Fknow is his actions resulted in this
OL,11,Flittle boy's death.
OL,13,F"To install a spy camera as Paula
OL,14,FRoberts did, means there must have
OL,15,Fbeen concerns about him.
OL,17,F"If you have concerns about those
OL,18,Fcaring for your children, you must
OL,19,Fact, speak out or ask for help.
